{"tid":1466964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"切忌互相指責。","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:41.000Z","uid":143981,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"56939f085bc9f2ac99e750014a8dc18a7ce7dbd3","tid":1466964,"uid":143981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"今晚機場活動已經令外國媒體，遊客對我地既行動有所保留。再加上中計，港共肯定會食住個勢，指責我地。好擔心市民睇到新聞畫面，會轉為指責我地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如今都中計，諗下點樣做返好個文宣啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好浪費時間互屌啦香港人，對準問題，要求政府回應五大訴求，不成功便成仁。"},{"pid":"f8174c63219ab75b592c03515f4e0fb153940560","tid":1466964,"uid":143981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"e5215402732df7e2e009d29964971a6cfddbdaaf","tid":1466964,"uid":140049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa9171d42a067866afc33e7ee6135e95841dcc1b","tid":1466964,"uid":75338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"［置頂］［緊急］ 民間記者會請幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466254</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3693f2c7091b2172a0649671307230806f2e26f9","tid":1466964,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba7aa5c9e294bfde4a08e80ce49defe14c456e3","tid":1466964,"uid":5812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聽日一定要做！！！！<br />\n<br />\n理撚得佢有冇鬼！！！！<br />\n<br />\n讓條路俾旅客，然後禮貌鞠躬道歉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n今晚大家早d翻去，準備文宣！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"aa4efe4054d7de093321e9148df59e7a5579cad4","tid":1466964,"uid":85498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家要繼續團結<br />\n點解星期一咁多人 係因為我地對政府 黑警都好憤怒<br />\n<br />\n我地會擔心勇武手足受傷、被捕。亦希望爭取更多民意去推倒政府<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足會用盡一切辦法保護其他手足 同時用不同手段去打倒政權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手法不同 但係理念一致<br />\n團結一致先能夠戰勝對方</span>"},{"pid":"fef1e26e43f99e5cf29d21c9d5293817db19d6cc","tid":1466964,"uid":143981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"切忌互屌啊各位，辛苦兩個月，如今互相指責，點對得住付出生命與前途去捍衛香港既義士。"},{"pid":"5df80cf2eab63f3d4164a7971cd4e876f8835346","tid":1466964,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef1e26e43f99e5cf29d21c9d5293817db19d6cc","tid":1466964,"uid":143981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"切忌互屌啊各位，辛苦兩個月，如今互相指責，點對得住付出生命與前途去捍衛香港既義士。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"機場和平d"},{"pid":"14041a3977e1db5b34a338c7be29eddab785ee2e","tid":1466964,"uid":143981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"「示威者在這兩個月來真是疲於奔命，很多休息時間都沒有，其實真是很辛苦。我們有時都要體諒，有時那一刻電光火石，影響判斷，有時出現誤中，都是不以為奇的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」"},{"pid":"11451e7220a1cfaa3a9e38da638797d6fda8a7fa","tid":1466964,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:07.000Z","msg":"補救先係重點呀 不分不割"},{"pid":"a12b87bedf2ef6dc7c77b267b07c3e3477fb49ad","tid":1466964,"uid":187387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[文宣] 公安單野..........<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDChtS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDChtS</a>"},{"pid":"e19aad55a0f7b9d61747f516a3a0fa877b894880","tid":1466964,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor